headline: Seagate Technology Holdings (NasdaqGS:STX) Stock Jumps 11% Over Past Week
summary: Seagate Technology Holdings (NasdaqGS:STX) experienced an 11% increase in its stock price over the past week. This rise comes despite a challenging week for the broader tech sector, including declines led by Nvidia, Tesla, and others. While major indexes such as the S&P 500 and Nasdaq Composite were down, Seagate's stock showed resilience.
